{"id":16868,"date":"2024-04-23T07:58:11","date_gmt":"2024-04-23T07:58:11","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/marketking.app\/?p=16868"},"modified":"2025-04-09T10:13:20","modified_gmt":"2025-04-09T10:13:20","slug":"marketking-v2-7-cashback-to-wallet-extra-packaging-charge","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/marketking.app\/blog\/marketking-v2-7-cashback-to-wallet-extra-packaging-charge\/","title":{"rendered":"MarketKing v2.7: Cashback to Wallet &amp; Extra Packaging Charge"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The <a href=\"https:\/\/codecanyon.net\/item\/marketking-multivendor-food-grocery-ecommerce-parcel-pharmacy-delivery-app-with-admin-website\/36772112\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/codecanyon.net\/item\/marketking-multivendor-food-grocery-ecommerce-parcel-pharmacy-delivery-app-with-admin-website\/36772112\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MarketKing<\/a> team brings another exciting news for its existing and new users with the release of version 2.7.&nbsp; The new version brings a fresh wave of features designed specifically to level up the multi vendor delivery business experience. This update is packed with improvements for everyone involved \u2013 admins, stores, and customers alike.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><br>So let\u2019s check all the incredible additions waiting for you at MarketKing!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Feature Lists of MarketKing v2.7:&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Cashback to wallet&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Block\/Unblock email for users<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Product-wise prescription handling during checkout&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Halal tag option<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Extra packaging charge<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Manage POS customer as a regular customer&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Module-wise product sorting<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Discount on first order<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2699\ufe0f Brand option for e-commerce<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\u2019s take a deeper look into these updates below-&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cashback to wallet<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Admins can now reward customers with cashback directly sent to their wallets. Admin has the flexible control to define the cashback type ( percentage or fixed amount), set the campaign duration, and choose customers manually or offer to all users.<br><br>If multiple cashback offers are active, customers automatically receive the one with the highest value!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With a cashback offer, there\u2019s a possibility to drive repeat purchases and customer engagement. Also, admins can create targeted campaigns to attract specific customer segments.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"544\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/cashback-to-wallet.webp\" alt=\"Cashback to wallet Feature\" class=\"wp-image-16869\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/cashback-to-wallet.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/cashback-to-wallet-300x179.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/cashback-to-wallet-768x459.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Admin Panel&gt; Promotion Management&gt; Cashback<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Important Note:<\/strong>&nbsp; To be eligible for cashback rewards, customers must be registered and have the &#8220;wallet option enabled in the system.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the customers&#8217; end they will be able to view all the cashback offers on the home page like this \u2b07\ufe0f<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-medium\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"293\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/cashback-1-300x293.webp\" alt=\"Get Reward Feature\" class=\"wp-image-16870\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/cashback-1-300x293.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/cashback-1-768x750.webp 768w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/cashback-1.webp 911w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Flutter Web App&gt;Home Page&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>And when a customer places an order there will be a pop-up message to notify them about the cashback offer with the value details \u2b07\ufe0f<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"294\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/cashback-1-1.webp\" alt=\"Cashback back after completing order feature\" class=\"wp-image-16871\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/cashback-1-1.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/cashback-1-1-300x97.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/cashback-1-1-768x248.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Flutter Web App&gt;Checkout Page&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>Explore: <a href=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/multi-vendor-marketplace-software-project-live-demo\/\">Multi Vendor Marketplace Software Project Live Demo<\/a><\/strong><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Block\/Unblock email for users<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now with MarketKing admin has greater control over user accounts. The Block\/Unblock functionality allows them to effortlessly manage customer, store, and delivery man access to the platform.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The process is remarkably straightforward. From the customer list, the admin can seamlessly block or unblock customer accounts using the &#8220;Active\/Inactive&#8221; toggle. Likewise, they can block or unblock stores and delivery men in the same manner.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"587\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/block-unblock-1.webp\" alt=\"User Block and Unblock email for users feature\" class=\"wp-image-16872\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/block-unblock-1.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/block-unblock-1-300x193.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/block-unblock-1-768x495.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Admin Panel&gt; Users&gt;Customer Management&gt;Customers<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>One thing to mention is that the email templates are customizable. Find the email templates for each user under the \u201cAccount Suspend\u201d and \u201cAccount Unsuspend\u201d tab.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"926\" height=\"605\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/block-unblock-email-template-3.webp\" alt=\"Account suspend email feature\" class=\"wp-image-16873\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/block-unblock-email-template-3.webp 926w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/block-unblock-email-template-3-300x196.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/block-unblock-email-template-3-768x502.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 926px) 100vw, 926px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Admin Panel&gt;System Management&gt;Email Template<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Through this feature, the admin can maintain a healthy user base and ensure a positive platform. Each action taken by the admin for this feature triggers an automated email notification to the affected user to keep them informed about their account status.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Product-wise prescription handling during checkout&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Admins and store owners can now designate specific medicines as &#8220;Prescription Required\u201d while adding or updating any item. This option is only available for the \u201cPharmacy\u201d module.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"578\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/prescription-required-1.webp\" alt=\"Product-wise prescription handling during checkout\u00a0Feature\" class=\"wp-image-16874\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/prescription-required-1.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/prescription-required-1-300x190.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/prescription-required-1-768x487.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Admin Panel&gt;Pharmacy Module&gt;Product Management&gt;Product Setup&gt;List&gt;Edit Item<\/em>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the customer&#8217;s end, products requiring a prescription will be marked with a &#8220;Prescription Required&#8221; warning.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"553\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/prescription-required-3-customer-end.webp\" alt=\"prescription required UX View\" class=\"wp-image-16875\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/prescription-required-3-customer-end.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/prescription-required-3-customer-end-300x182.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/prescription-required-3-customer-end-768x466.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Flutter Web App&gt;Pharmacy Module&gt; Item Details<\/em>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>During checkout, customers attempting to purchase prescription medication will be prompted to upload a clear image of their valid prescription.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-medium\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"267\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/prescription-5-customer-checkout--300x267.webp\" alt=\"Upload prescription during checkout\u00a0\" class=\"wp-image-16876\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/prescription-5-customer-checkout--300x267.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/prescription-5-customer-checkout--768x685.webp 768w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/prescription-5-customer-checkout-.webp 911w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path: <\/em><\/strong><em>Flutter Web Application&gt;Checkout Page&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This feature ensures customers only receive medication with proper authorization.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Halal tag option<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you can serve customers seeking halal options through this feature. This feature is only available for the \u201cGrocery\u201d and \u201cFood\u201d modules.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>While adding or updating items, admins, and restaurants\/stores can easily check the &#8220;Is It Halal&#8221; tag for relevant products through the \u201cItem Details\u201d section \u2b07\ufe0f<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"581\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/halal-1.webp\" alt=\"Halal tag option\" class=\"wp-image-16877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/halal-1.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/halal-1-300x191.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/halal-1-768x490.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path: <\/em><\/strong><em>Admin Panel&gt;Food Module&gt;Food Management&gt;Food Setup&gt;List&gt;Edit Item<\/em>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Products marked as &#8220;Halal&#8221; will display a Halal-certified logo on the customer-facing product details page.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-medium\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"236\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/halal-2-300x236.webp\" alt=\"Halal tag option customer view\" class=\"wp-image-16878\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/halal-2-300x236.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/halal-2-768x604.webp 768w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/halal-2.webp 911w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path: <\/em><\/strong><em>Flutter Web Application&gt;Food Module&gt;Item Details<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With this feature, you can show a commitment towards inclusivity and customer satisfaction. Customers with certain dietary preferences and requirements will benefit from it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>Also Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/blog\/best-technology-stack-for-ecommerce-website\/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/blog\/best-technology-stack-for-ecommerce-website\/\">Best Technology Stack for eCommerce Website Development<\/a><\/strong><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Extra packaging charge<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With this extra packaging charge feature customers will get their orders delivered in a more secure and presentable way and store owners will be able to generate a few more bucks.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Admin can define which modules will allow the extra packaging charge option from the business settings.&nbsp;<br><strong>Note:<\/strong> This feature is available for the \u201cGrocery\u201d, \u201cFood\u201d, \u201cPharmacy\u201d and \u201cEcommerce\u201d modules.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"306\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/extra-packaging-1.webp\" alt=\"Extra packaging charge\" class=\"wp-image-16879\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/extra-packaging-1.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/extra-packaging-1-300x101.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/extra-packaging-1-768x258.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Admin Panel&gt;Business Settings&gt;Order Settings<\/em>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Stores have complete control to set the charge and enable\/disable this option as per their business requirements. This will be solely the store\u2019s income.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-medium\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"154\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/extra-packaging-2-300x154.webp\" alt=\"Extra packaging charge amount\" class=\"wp-image-16880\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/extra-packaging-2-300x154.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/extra-packaging-2-768x394.webp 768w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/extra-packaging-2.webp 911w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Store Panel&gt; Business Section&gt;Store Config<\/em>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>During checkout, customers can easily choose to add extra packaging for their order with a simple checkbox. The extra packaging charge will be clearly displayed at checkout to help customers make an informed decision while purchasing.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-medium\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"271\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/extra-packaging-3-271x300.webp\" alt=\"Extra packaging charge product checkout details\" class=\"wp-image-16881\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/extra-packaging-3-271x300.webp 271w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/extra-packaging-3-768x850.webp 768w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/extra-packaging-3.webp 911w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 271px) 100vw, 271px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Flutter Web Application&gt; Checkout Page<\/em>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Manage POS customer as a regular customer<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Customers added through the POS system (both by admins and stores) are now automatically treated as regular customers within MarketKing. Newly created POS customers will receive a welcome email with a dummy password. The email will go from the email template section under the \u201cCustomer Mail Templates\u201d on the &#8220;POS New Customer Registration&#8221; tab.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Admins have the flexibility to enable or disable this feature based on their specific workflow preferences.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"909\" height=\"597\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/poscustomer-1-1.webp\" alt=\"Manage POS customer as a regular customer feature\" class=\"wp-image-16882\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/poscustomer-1-1.webp 909w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/poscustomer-1-1-300x197.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/poscustomer-1-1-768x504.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 909px) 100vw, 909px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Admin Panel&gt;System Management&gt;Email Template<\/em>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Module-wise product sorting<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This innovative feature empowers users to personalize their browsing experience and discover products that align with their specific interests.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>After signing up, a one-time pop-up will guide new users through setting their preferred sorting options for each module.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"610\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/module-wise-product-sorting.webp\" alt=\"Module-wise product sorting feature\" class=\"wp-image-16883\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/module-wise-product-sorting.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/module-wise-product-sorting-300x201.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/module-wise-product-sorting-768x514.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Flutter Web Application&gt;Sign Up<\/em>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This personalized sorting ensures that the product listings displayed on the homepage better reflect each customer&#8217;s unique preferences.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Discount on first order<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now the referral bonus can be enjoyed on both sides with this amazing update of MarketKing.&nbsp; Both existing customers sharing their referral code and new users signing up with the code can enjoy this reward.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Admins have complete control over activating or deactivating the &#8220;Customer Can Earn &amp; Buy From Referral&#8221; option.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"928\" height=\"255\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/referal-admin-customer-setup-1.webp\" alt=\"Discount on first order feature\" class=\"wp-image-16884\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/referal-admin-customer-setup-1.webp 928w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/referal-admin-customer-setup-1-300x82.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/referal-admin-customer-setup-1-768x211.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 928px) 100vw, 928px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path: <\/em><\/strong><em>Admin Panel&gt;Business Settings&gt;Customers<\/em>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Admins have complete control over the referral program. They can set the &#8220;Earning Per Referral USD&#8221; value for referring customers.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Admins can independently enable\/disable the referral discount for new users. They can further customize the reward by setting the discount amount, type (percentage or fixed amount ), and duration (validity period).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"580\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/referal-admin-customer-setup-3.webp\" alt=\"Customer referral earnings settings \" class=\"wp-image-16885\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/referal-admin-customer-setup-3.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/referal-admin-customer-setup-3-300x191.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/referal-admin-customer-setup-3-768x489.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Admin Panel&gt;&gt;Business Settings&gt;Customers<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Existing customers can share their unique referral code with friends and family.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"621\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-share.webp\" alt=\"Refer and Earn Feature\" class=\"wp-image-16886\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-share.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-share-300x205.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-share-768x524.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Flutter Web Application&gt;Menu&gt;Refer &amp; Earn<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>New users signing up with a referral code receive a warm welcome message highlighting their bonus details \u2b07\ufe0f<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"507\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-new-customer-welcome-message.webp\" alt=\"New users signing up with a referral code receive a warm welcome message\" class=\"wp-image-16887\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-new-customer-welcome-message.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-new-customer-welcome-message-300x167.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-new-customer-welcome-message-768x427.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>During their first order checkout, new users will receive a pop-up message confirming the applied referral discount on their order summary.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"556\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-new-customer-pop-up-message.webp\" alt=\"confirming the applied referral discount on their order summary\" class=\"wp-image-16888\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-new-customer-pop-up-message.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-new-customer-pop-up-message-300x183.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-new-customer-pop-up-message-768x469.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"790\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-new-customer-Referal-Discount-added-on-first-order-790x1024.webp\" alt=\"confirming the applied referral discount on their order summary-1\" class=\"wp-image-16889\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-new-customer-Referal-Discount-added-on-first-order-790x1024.webp 790w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-new-customer-Referal-Discount-added-on-first-order-231x300.webp 231w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-new-customer-Referal-Discount-added-on-first-order-768x996.webp 768w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/refer-code-new-customer-Referal-Discount-added-on-first-order.webp 911w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 790px) 100vw, 790px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Flutter Web Application&gt;Checkout Page<\/em>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Brand option for eCommerce<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This feature is designed exclusively for the eCommerce or shop module.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Admins can now categorize products under dedicated brands, giving customers a clear overview of available options. They have the complete freedom to activate or deactivate brands based on specific business needs and policies.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"587\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/brand-setup-1.webp\" alt=\"Brand option for eCommerce\" class=\"wp-image-16891\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/brand-setup-1.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/brand-setup-1-300x193.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/brand-setup-1-768x495.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path: <\/em><\/strong><em>Admin Panel&gt;Shop Module&gt;Product Management&gt;Brands&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Customers can easily discover and explore products from their favorite brands with a dedicated &#8220;Brand&#8221; section on the \u201cShop\u201d module homepage.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"911\" height=\"298\" src=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/brand-setup-2.webp\" alt=\"Home page Brand option for eCommerce \" class=\"wp-image-16892\" srcset=\"https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/brand-setup-2.webp 911w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/brand-setup-2-300x98.webp 300w, https:\/\/marketking.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/brand-setup-2-768x251.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 911px) 100vw, 911px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong><em>Path:<\/em><\/strong><em> Flutter Web Application&gt;Shop Module&gt;Home Page&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This section provides customers with easy access to their favorite brands, enhancing their browsing and shopping experience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Other Improvements<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some other essential improvements that have been done in version 2.7 to ensure a seamless and optimized user experience-&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Enhanced User Interface and content across the apps<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Resolved issues for a smoother experience<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Improved Queries and Optimized Performance<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Compatibility with the latest Flutter SDK 3.19.5&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>That\u2019s all from this release. Stay tuned to get all the latest release news and updates before anyone.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The MarketKing team brings another exciting news for its existing and new users with the release of version 2.7.&nbsp; The new version brings a fresh wave of features designed specifically to level up the multi vendor delivery business experience. This update 